µC0Critikill:µC4 Inside: µC2MadeµC4, µC2CougarµC4, µC2CycloneµC4, µC2FacetµC4, µC2ProwlerµC4 and many many more. Outside the scene: too many to count. A lot of writers and graffiti artist, designers and painters from different sections. I also had much love for typography and urban art.

µC0Ghandy:µC3 You also work professionally as a graphic designer, did your time in the scene help you with that? What exactly do you do for a living, please tell us.

