µC0Critikill:µC4 I founded it with µC2JadeµC4 during corona to have an exchange about...

Jade and I came up with the idea that it would be nice to form a pixel art group, we thought that 16 bit platforms and 16 colours would be a nice theme for the name. Also we were all about 16 years old at the time when we got into the demoscene. So the name µC2SWEET16 (S16)µC4 was born.

